#: ../../../lib/web/src/components/restore-banner.tsx:82
msgid "Your account was moved here from {source}. Until you delete it there, messages and notifications may reach both servers, some of your content keeps being served from the old server, and followers may take a few minutes to find you here."
msgstr "Ang iyong account ay inilipat dito mula sa {source}. Hanggang hindi mo ito binubura doon, ang mga mensahe at abiso ay maaaring maabot ang parehong mga server, ang ilan sa iyong nilalaman ay patuloy na pinaglilingkuran mula sa lumang server, at ang mga tagasunod ay maaaring maglaan ng ilang minuto upang mahanap ka dito."

#: src/features/user/close-account.tsx:116
msgid "Your account will be permanently deleted on {purgeDate}. You've been signed out. To cancel, sign in again before then."
msgstr "Permanenteng buburahin ang iyong account sa {purgeDate}. Naka-sign out ka na. Upang kanselahin, mag-sign in muli bago ang petsang iyon."

#: src/features/user/close-account.tsx:84
msgid "Your account will be scheduled for deletion and you'll be signed out. You can cancel any time before the deletion date by logging back in. Download your data first if you want to keep a copy."
msgstr "Itatakda nang burahin ang iyong account at masa-sign out ka. Maaari mong kanselahin anumang oras bago ang petsa ng pagbura sa pamamagitan ng muling pag-log in. I-download muna ang iyong data kung nais mong magtago ng kopya."

#: src/features/user/replication.tsx:194
msgid "Your account's data on this server will be permanently deleted and you'll be signed out here. Your account stays on your other servers, and you can re-add this one later."
msgstr "Permanenteng tatanggalin ang data ng iyong account sa server na ito at masa-sign out ka rito. Mananatili ang iyong account sa iba mong mga server, at maaari mong idagdag muli ito sa ibang pagkakataon."

